nceramente%20de%20amarlos%20y%20perdonarlos%2C%20pero%20honestamente%20prefiero%20mantener%20mi%20distancia.%0D%0A%0D%0APensar%20en%20tener%20que%20estar%20juntos%20para%20siempre%20como%20familia%20me%20parece%20terrible.%20%C2%BFMe%20podr%C3%ADas%20dar%20alg%C3%BAn%20consejo%3F%0D%0ARespuesta%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0ALamento%20mucho%20lo%20que%20est%C3%A1s%20pasando.%0D%0A%0D%0AEl%20primer%20consejo%20que%20te%20ofrecer%C3%ADa%20es%20que%20le%20preguntes%20al%20Se%C3%B1or%20mediante%20mucho%20estudio%2C%20meditaci%C3%B3n%2C%20ayuno%20y%20oraci%C3%B3n%20si%20realmente%20son%20el%20tipo%20de%20personas%20que%20el%20Se%C3%B1or%20considerar%C3%ADa%20%E2%80%9Ct%C3%B3xicas%E2%80%9D.%0D%0A%0D%0ALa%20vara%20con%20la%20que%20mides%20deber%C3%ADa%20ser%20la%20siguiente%3A%0D%0A1.%20%C2%BFLos%20miembros%20de%20tu%20familia%20te%20est%C3%A1n%20alejando%20continuamente%20del%20Se%C3%B1or%20y%20de%20Sus%20bendiciones%20que%20cuando%20te%20encuentras%20solo%3F%0D%0A2.%20Por%20cada%20invitaci%C3%B3n%20que%20te%20hacen%2C%20%C2%BFte%20encuentras%20m%C3%A1s%20cerca%20o%20m%C3%A1s%20lejos%20del%20Se%C3%B1or%3F%0D%0A3.%20Por%20cada%20invitaci%C3%B3n%20que%20aceptan%20de%20ti%2C%20%C2%BFse%20encuentran%20ellos%20m%C3%A1s%20cerca%20o%20m%C3%A1s%20lejos%20del%20Se%C3%B1or%3F%0D%0AEspero%20que%20sepas%20cu%C3%A1les%20deber%C3%ADan%20ser%20las%20respuestas.%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0ASi%20es%20una%20familia%20realmente%20t%C3%B3xica%2C%20entonces%20s%C3%AD%2C%20mant%C3%A9n%20tu%20distancia.%20Ojo%2C%20esta%20no%20es%20una%20excusa%20para%20odiarlos.%20No%20son%20solo%20tu%20familia%2C%20ellos%20son%20hijos%20de%20Dios.%0D%0A%0D%0ASiempre%20debemos%20esperar%20lo%20mejor%20de%20las%20personas%2C%20pero%20si%20su%20veneno%20es%20m%C3%A1s%20poderoso%20de%20lo%20que%20tus%20reservas%20espirituales%20pueden%20soportar%2C%20entonces%2C%20deber%C3%A1s%20mantenerte%20a%20salvo.%0D%0A%0D%0AEl%20Se%C3%B1or%20nos%20dio%20el%20mandamiento%20de%20amar%20a%20nuestro%20pr%C3%B3jimo%20como%20a%20nosotros%20mismos.%20%C2%BFNo%20significa%20eso%20que%20necesitas%20amarte%20a%20ti%20mismo%20primero%3F%20S%C3%AD%2C%20es%20verdad.%20Muchas%20personas%20que%20carecen%20de%20amor%20y%20compasi%C3%B3n%20por%20los%20dem%C3%A1s%20tambi%C3%A9n%20son%20personas%20que%20carecen%20de%20caridad%20y%20compasi%C3%B3n%20por%20s%C3%AD%20mismos.%0D%0A%0D%0AEl%20Se%C3%B1or%20tambi%C3%A9n%20nos%20dio%20el%20mandamiento%20de%20quitar%20la%20viga%20de%20nuestros%20propios%20ojos%20antes%20de%20que%20podamos%20quitar%20la%20paja%20del%20ojo%20de%20nuestro%20hermano.%20Si%20bien%20esto%20hace%20una%20referencia%20directa%20a%20la%20hipocres%C3%ADa%2C%20yo%20lo%20aplicar%C3%ADa%20de%20manera%20diferente%20a%20tu%20situaci%C3%B3n.%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0ASi%20tus%20reservas%20espirituales%20est%C3%A1n%20demasiado%20bajas%2C%20no%20podr%C3%A1s%20ser%20una%20fuente%20de%20inspiraci%C3%B3n%20para%20los%20dem%C3%A1s.%20Cuando%20hayas%20llegado%20a%20un%20punto%20de%20tu%20vida%20donde%20tu%20esp%C3%ADritu%20sea%20lo%20suficientemente%20fuerte%20como%20para%20%E2%80%9Crecibir%20los%20golpes%E2%80%9D%20de%20estar%20con%20un%20grupo%20t%C3%B3xico%20al%20que%20se%20supone%20que%20debes%20ayudar%2C%20entonces%20deber%C3%A1s%20hacer%20todo%20lo%20posible%20para%20atraerlos%20a%20la%20luz%20del%20Salvador.%0D%0A%0D%0AMi%20%C3%BAltimo%20consejo%20ser%C3%ADa%20que%20a%20pesar%20de%20todo%20los%20ames%2C%20siempre%20%C3%A1malos%2C%20desea%20lo%20mejor%20para%20ellos%20y%20ora%20por%20su%20bienestar.%20No%20son%20perfectos%2C%20al%20igual%20que%20nosotros%2C%20pero%20son%20tu%20familia.%0D%0A%0D%0AFuente%3A%20Askgramps%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0ATambi%C3%A9n%20te%20puede%20interesar%0D%0A%0D%0A%20%09Sin%20exaltaci%C3%B3n%2C%20a%C3%BAn%3A%20La%20frustraci%C3%B3n%20de%20estar%20soltero%20en%20una%20Iglesia%20centrada%20en%20la%20familia%0D%0A%20%09%C2%BFC%C3%B3mo%20puedo%20ayudar%20a%20mis%20familiares%20y%20amigos%20que%20han%20dejado%20la%20Iglesia%3F%0D%0A%20%09Familia%20eterna%3A%20%C2%BFTraer%20hijos%20al%20mundo%20es%20un%20c